Description: Symfony DependencyInjection component (6.x backport for forky)
 Allows you to standardize and centralize the way objects are constructed
 in your application.
 .
 This is a backport of Symfony 6.4.x for Debian forky, providing the 6.x
 series for applications that have not yet migrated to Symfony 7.
